&lt;p>I am very much looking forward to it.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Registration information will be announced soon. Follow &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/Women_MIR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@Women_MIR&lt;/a> to not miss any news.&lt;/p>
